proof
let p;
set n = ( len p );
A1: ( dom p ) = ( Seg ( len p ) ) by FINSEQ_1:def 3;
A2: ( Indices ( CCirc p ) ) = [: ( Seg n ),( Seg n ) :] by MATRIX_1:24;
assume A3: p is  first-col-of-circulant;
then A4: ( CCirc p ) is_col_circulant_about p by CKB13:def 1;
( - p ) is  first-col-of-circulant by A3,CKB51:1;
then A5: ( CCirc ( - p ) ) is_col_circulant_about ( - p ) by CKB13:def 1;
p is (Element of ( ( len p ) -tuples_on (the carrier of K) )) by FINSEQ_2:92;
then ( - p ) is (Element of ( ( len p ) -tuples_on (the carrier of K) )) by FINSEQ_2:113;
then A6: ( len ( - p ) ) = ( len p ) by CARD_1:def 7;
